01:49.235 --> 01:53.114
Yes, it is. I have Global Entry.
Where's the pre-check line?

01:53.448 --> 01:55.200
It is right over there, ma'am.
Leave your shoes on.

01:55.366 --> 01:57.243
- No need to take your laptop out.
- Oh.

01:57.494 --> 01:59.496
Is it all right if I go with her? Uh...

01:59.662 --> 02:01.706
- I'm a cop, so...
- Do you have Global Entry?

02:02.540 --> 02:05.210
- No.
- Then you can't go with her.

02:08.379 --> 02:10.173
I'll just see you on the other side, okay?

02:15.220 --> 02:17.055
- Sir?
- Yeah...

02:20.058 --> 02:22.227
<i>This way, please. Single file.</i>

02:35.824 --> 02:37.116
Arms up, please.

02:46.584 --> 02:49.295
- Your watch.
- Oh, shit. Sorry.

02:53.132 --> 02:55.051
Just walk on around. Come back through.

03:03.726 --> 03:05.186
- Enjoy your flight.
- Thank you.

03:12.443 --> 03:14.445
<i>Come on. Hey, give it back.
You can't take it, no.</i>

03:14.612 --> 03:16.781
<i>- Look, no, no. No, you can't take it.
- Sir.</i>

03:16.948 --> 03:18.616
- No, it's my suit.
- Is there a problem here, sir?

03:18.783 --> 03:20.451
No, look,
it's not on the list of restricted items.

03:20.618 --> 03:22.412
Okay, look, there's gonna be
a nuclear event,

03:22.579 --> 03:24.664
and I'm entitled
to protect myself from fallout.

03:24.831 --> 03:26.708
<i>Okay? I'm missing my flight.</i>

03:26.875 --> 03:28.543
I need to get to Antarctica.

03:28.710 --> 03:30.044
I need to get to Antarctica!

03:33.089 --> 03:34.549
Another one bites the dust.

03:54.235 --> 03:55.236
Hey.

03:56.029 --> 03:57.071
Hi.

04:00.867 --> 04:02.160
Everything go okay?

04:02.535 --> 04:03.995
Yeah, absolutely.

04:04.412 --> 04:05.997
- You?
- Great.

04:07.999 --> 04:09.083
What are you smuggling?

04:10.001 --> 04:11.085
Sorry?

04:11.502 --> 04:12.670
