04:19.385 --> 04:22.388
I have $20,000 in cash
strapped to my body.

04:32.065 --> 04:34.484
- Lock the door.
- What are you doing?

04:36.194 --> 04:37.987
I borrowed your duct tape.

04:38.696 --> 04:41.741
