04:49.707 --> 04:52.585
Huh. Help me get the tape off?

04:58.675 --> 05:00.051
Ooh.

05:03.221 --> 05:04.389
Ooh.

05:04.973 --> 05:06.849
You hiding anything else
you wanna tell me about?

05:08.893 --> 05:10.019
Maybe.

05:46.764 --> 05:48.683
<i>- How many?
- A hundred and nineteen.</i>

05:49.183 --> 05:50.184
<i>Jesus.</i>

05:50.351 --> 05:51.436
<i>They made these testimonials.</i>

05:51.602 --> 05:53.396
<i>They're standing there,
holding a newspaper</i>

05:53.563 --> 05:55.481
<i>like a hostage video.</i>

05:56.107 --> 05:58.276
<i>They, they gave their names,
so I looked them up</i>

05:58.443 --> 05:59.527
<i>just to see if any of them
were still around</i>

05:59.694 --> 06:01.904
<i>after they supposedly got into this thing.</i>

06:02.697 --> 06:05.283
<i>The thing that zaps them
with the radiation?</i>

06:05.450 --> 06:08.286
<i>Yes, honey, the thing
that zaps them with the radiation.</i>

06:10.455 --> 06:11.622
