06:22.300 --> 06:25.053
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,
the seat belt sign is now turned off,</i>

06:25.219 --> 06:27.013
<i>and you are free to move about the cabin.</i>

06:28.473 --> 06:30.558
So it's a sting operation.

06:30.725 --> 06:32.643
