12:04.767 --> 12:06.811
<i>Now, how are you with a spatula?</i>

12:06.977 --> 12:08.145
<i>You know, can you flip 'em?</i>

12:08.312 --> 12:10.481
<i>- What kind of question is that?
- Well, it's tricky.</i>

13:23.888 --> 13:26.557
<i>And I sure hope no one watching
is named Kevin.</i>

13:26.724 --> 13:27.725
<i>Why is that, Pam?</i>

13:27.892 --> 13:29.143
<i>Well, apparently, there's not one,</i>

13:29.310 --> 13:32.480
<i>but two missing Kevins
